        "TileImage": "$($repository a2429d84-2b78-42c4-a88d-82b8984ca92d).Image",
        "Description": "They&apos;re here, 47. Senator Angus Pritchard is pretending to be a board member to infiltrate our facility. A dozen of his wretched associates are scattered across the quartier to take us down. Kill Angus and a few of his men. If you need more weapons, our underground facility ought to have what you need. Our code is 0118. Act quick, 47. ICA&apos;s fate is in your hands.",
